Package: kmod-wireguard
Version: 6.12-rc2-r1
Depends: kernel (=6.12-rc2~d72a8c342a550c9a4cef1f799a1e10de-r1), kmod-crypto-lib-chacha20poly1305, kmod-crypto-lib-curve25519, kmod-udptunnel4, kmod-udptunnel6
